<TEXT>
<P>
 The city of Oxnard has filed a lawsuit against the Santa Barbara Civic Light 
Opera seeking nearly $47,000 in unpaid bills for the use of the Oxnard Civic 
Auditorium, according to court records. 
</P>
<P>
 The suit says the opera failed to pay for using the auditorium in June, 1991. 
