<P>
 Tips on the identities of two masked gunmen who robbed a Thousand Oaks 
pizzeria could bring tipsters a reward of up to $1,000 from Ventura County 
Crime Stoppers Inc. 
</P>
<P>
 Two heavyset, masked gunmen entered the Lamppost Pizza restaurant on Lindero 
Canyon Road on July 30, held guns to two employees' heads and forced them to 
open a safe before fleeing with cash.No one was hurt in the robbery. 
</P>
