DREAM TEAM II WINS FEW FRIENDS FOR ITS OBNOXIOUS BEHAVIOR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Dream team? More like our worst nightmare. 
</P>
<P>
 Once again, a bunch of headstrong, trash-talking basketball players from the 
United States has shown the world why our country has so many problems.Whatever 
happened to respect, dignity and sportsmanship? This in-your-face tactic to 
embarrass your opponent is against everything my parents taught me about 
sports. 
</P>
<P>
 I can live with the idea that these jerks can continue to play professional 
sports. I just won't watch. But let's try to represent our country with a great 
team of respectful players and show the world what we want to become, not what 
we are, a bunch of disrespectful, arrogant jerks. 
</P>
<P>
 G. BAKER 
